Element - Class in world
the building blocks of the world, all things in the world are elements, an element is defaulty of neutral ownership

a reference of each element is given to all classes that would modify those elements, when one of the class declares the element to be dead all classes remove their respective references to the element and thus it is effectively removed from the game
